{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources to expand and upgrade your base. Automate defenses and resource production to create a self-sufficient stronghold in a post-apocalyptic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/uppergif.gif?t=1732137498\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Build Your Base</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform your campsite into a fortified base, complete with upgradable structures to keep the zombies at bay and provide for your survival needs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/build.gif?t=1732137498\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survive in a Dangerous World</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loot and explore an open world filled with valuable weapons, food, and supplies. Face the ever-present threat of zombie hordes and watch out for other scavengers who may be lurking in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/world.gif?t=1732137498\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customize Your Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from hundreds of customization options to create your ideal character.<br><br><strong>Upcoming Features Coming (Completed by May 2025)</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A new story with new characters, dialogue, decisions and tons of new objectives, with multiple endings and events that effect the surrounding map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improved enemy and friendly character AI</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Three large new map locations, including a mall, a farm, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Updated perimeter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New items including grenades, walkie-talkie, and new story items</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Happy Camper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2236240/80a6f14ee0a18faab5efdd07e8c5ec07067ee7b2.jpg"},{"name":"Zombie Magnet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2236240/f9e37832fb360e7b322d0ecfa075c32be104443f.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor of the Apocalypse","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2236240/265b224dbc19964f26fea31e6469b3b861d9b092.jpg"},{"name":"Scavenger Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2236240/a80a44902058e5891accb05980ea2fb3ba4f90a7.jpg"}],"total":4},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2236240?t=1732137498","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2236240?t=1732137498","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732137498","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732137498","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2258820,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather resources to expand and upgrade your base. Automate defenses and resource production to create a self-sufficient stronghold in a post-apocalyptic world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2236240/extras/uppergif.gif?t=1732137498\" /></p><p cl